snippet.title: Warframe | The Jovian Concord Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Something sinister is stirring on Jupiter. 

Introducing The Jovian Concord. More than just a rework of Warframe's Gas City, experience completely reimagined graphics and gameplay. Infiltrate the remastered Corpus Gas City, drive your blade through Amalgam horrors, unlock the power of the Wisp Warframe, and shine a light on this Corpus plot. https://bit.ly/2K55wQP
